  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003EYour safety is our priority. In the event of severe weather conditions, natural disasters, or other emergencies that necessitate the closure of an office location, we will communicate decisions regarding office closures and work expectations promptly. We strive to ensure clarity and minimize disruption while prioritizing the well-being of our team.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
